<li><code>npm start</code>  </li>
<li>go to <a href="index.html">http://localhost:2368</a> in browser  </li>
<li>login and write post  </li>
<li><code>buster generate</code>  </li>
<li><code>buster preview</code>, and check in <a href="http://localhost:9000">http://localhost:9000</a>  </li>
